<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{أتبنون}</span> عَلَى الاسْتِفْهَامِ؛<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> قَدْ فَعَلْتُمْ <span class="c3">{بِكُل ريع}</span> بِكُلِّ فَجٍّ <span class="c3">{آيَةً}</span> أَيْ: عَلَمَا <span class="c3">{تعبثون}</span> أَيْ: تَلْعَبُونَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُحَمَّدٌ:</span> الرِّيعُ: الِارْتِفَاعُ مِنَ الْأَرْضِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الشَّمَّاخُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>